@startuml
actor "Manager" as MGR
boundary "UI Perhitungan" as UI
control "API /api/bwm/perhitungan" as API
control "BWM Engine\nlib/bwm/" as BWM
database "Supabase\n(PostgreSQL)" as DB

== LIST PENUGASAN SIAP HITUNG ==
MGR -> UI: Buka /manager/bwm/perhitungan
UI -> API: GET /api/manager/penugasan?status=Selesai
activate API
API -> DB: SELECT penugasan WHERE status='Selesai' ORDER BY id DESC
DB --> API: [{ id, judul, bwm_status, plafon_bonus, ... }]
API --> UI: { data: [...] }
deactivate API
UI -> MGR: Tampil daftar penugasan + status BWM

== HITUNG BWM ==
MGR -> UI: Pilih penugasan, klik "Hitung BWM"
UI -> API: POST /api/bwm/perhitungan { penugasan_id }
activate API

API -> DB: SELECT preferensi_bwm WHERE is_active=true LIMIT 1
DB --> API: { best_criteria, worst_criteria, bo_c1..bo_c5, ow_c1..ow_c5 }

API -> BWM: parsePreferensi(dbRow)
BWM --> API: ParsedPreferensi

API -> DB: SELECT penugasan_teknisi + profil + laporan_progres WHERE penugasan_id
note right: Ambil raw values c1..c5\nuntuk setiap teknisi
DB --> API: BWMInput[]

API -> BWM: batchCalculateBWM(inputs, parsedPreferensi)
activate BWM
note right
 1. solveBWM() -> bobot + xi*
 2. calculateBatchRanges()
 3. Normalisasi Min-Max
 4. calculateWSM() -> skor
 5. calculateTunjangan()
 6. Konsistensi CR
end note
BWM --> API: [{ input, result }]

API -> DB: INSERT INTO perhitungan_bwm (batch)
DB --> API: saved
API -> DB: UPDATE penugasan SET bwm_status='draft' WHERE id=$1
DB --> API: OK
API --> UI: { data: results }
deactivate API
UI -> MGR: Redirect ke /perhitungan/{id}

== REVIEW DETAIL ==
UI -> API: GET /api/bwm/perhitungan?penugasan_id=$1
activate API
API -> DB: SELECT perhitungan_bwm + profil WHERE penugasan_id=$1
DB --> API: [{ teknisi, c1..c5, w1..w5, skor_akhir, cr, status }]
API --> UI: { data }
deactivate API
UI -> MGR: Tampil skor, bobot, CR, tunjangan

== FINALISASI ==
MGR -> UI: Klik "Finalisasi Semua"
UI -> API: PATCH /api/bwm/perhitungan/{id}/finalize
loop for each perhitungan
  activate API
  API -> DB: UPDATE perhitungan_bwm SET status='final', finalisasi_oleh=$1, finalisasi_pada=NOW()
  note right
    Trigger on gaji_teknisi:
    INSERT + calculate_total_gaji()
  end note
  DB --> API: OK
  deactivate API
end
API -> DB: UPDATE penugasan SET bwm_status='final' WHERE id=$1
API --> UI: { message: "Semua perhitungan difinalisasi" }
UI -> MGR: Badge "Final" pada semua kartu
@enduml
